product.title: StyleCraft JetLiner Professional Hair Dryer, Ionic, 1600 Watts, Matte Grey
product.description: Stylecraft and Silver Bullet introduce the JetLiner cutting-edge long life digital brushless motor hair dryer, a game-changing tool that will revolutionize your hairstyling experience. Operating at an incredible 105,000 RPM, this motor delivers powerful and efficient performance, ensuring quick drying and styling. The digital display features 5 preset heat/speed settings designed specifically for fine, normal, and coarse hair, with a turbo mode for rapid drying and a manual mode for customized performance. With a total of 13 heat/speed settings available in manual mode, you can find the perfect temperature and airflow for every hair type. Experience salon-quality results with our Ionic Generator technology. This advanced feature seals the hair cuticle, creating a smooth and shiny finish while reducing frizz. Say goodbye to unruly hair and hello to a sleek and polished look that lasts. The professional 9 ft cord provides ample reach and flexibility during use, and the convenient hanging hook ensures easy storage when you're done. The auto-locking function ensures that your selected speed and heat settings remain consistent throughout your styling session, eliminating the frustration of accidental adjustments. Cleaning and maintenance are a breeze with the removable filter, allowing for easy removal of debris and hair. Additionally, an extra foam filter is included for added convenience. Never worry about losing your preferred settings again with the memory feature, which recalls your last used heat and speed settings. This time-saving feature ensures consistent and reliable results with each use. To top it all off, this hair dryer comes complete with two specialized styling nozzles and a diffuser, giving you the versatility to create a wide range of styles, from sleek and straight to bouncy and curly. Upgrade your hairstyling routine with our Long Life Digital Brushless Motor Hair Dryer and unlock endless possibilities for flawless hair every day. STYLECRAFT, THE ART & SCIENCE OF STYLING.
